These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up, fanta, lemonade, hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daisy, daffodil, balloon-flower, amaryllis, sunflower, dahlia, poppy
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is not the person who growsdahlia##6
 3. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person who growssunflower##5
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person who growsdaffodil##7
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who growsballoon-flower##7
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
11. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
13. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
14. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
15. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Beverage          | fanta    | mirinda    | 7up | milk | lemonade | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk |
| Flower   | sunflower | daisy | balloon-flower  | dahlia   | amaryllis    | daffodil | poppy |

