.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, whist, go, poker, scrabble, bridge
There are 7 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, american, russian, argentine, indian, turkish
 1. the indian is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the person playing backgammon##7
 2. the turkish is the person playing go##1
 3. the argentine is on the right of the turkish##1
 4. the turkish is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the russian and the egyptian##7
 6. the person playing scrabble is somewhere between the person playing go and the american##7
 7. the person playing poker is somewhere between the person playing go and the person playing backgammon##7
 8. the dutch is on the right of the russian##1
 9. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
10. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the indian##5
11. the indian is not the person playing bridge##6
12. the egyptian is on the right of the indian##1
13. the argentine is between the russian and the person playing go##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Game    | bridge  | whist | scrabble | go | mah-jongg     | poker | backgammon  |
| Nationality   | american | indian | egyptian  | turkish  | argentine | russian      | dutch |

