.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-3::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, june, november, july, april, february, december
There are 7 different favourite colors: purple, red, pink, brown, white, ebony, blue
 1. the person who likes blue is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who likes pink##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
 3. the person who likes red is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
 4. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ebony##5
 5. the person who likes purple is between the person who likes ebony and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 6. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere between the person who likes white and the person who likes blue##7
10. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
11. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
12. the person who's birthday is in april is not the person who likes purple##6
13. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in april##7
14. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
15. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
16. the person who's birthday is in april is not the person who likes ebony##6
17. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
18. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
19. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6     |      7      |
