 5. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
 8. the person playing monopoly is not the siglo-smoker##6
 9. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
10. the person playing canasta is not the siglo-smoker##6
