 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in november##7
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
10. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in august is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
