13. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's birthday is in january##2
14. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's sport is cycling##7
15. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
