 9. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is swimming is the person driving the airplane##1
12. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
13. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the car##1
14. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person driving the car##6
15. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere between the person driving the train and the person driving the boat##7
16. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
17. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the taxi##7

